{"tid":1565654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李嘉誠籲年輕人「顧全大局」  中共政法委：縱容犯罪","createTime":"2019-09-13T08:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T12:42:54.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b3fd617fde62be01d5404e199becdb6614e6b3eb","tid":1565654,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:41:07.000Z","msg":"長和資深顧問李嘉誠日前表示，政府應該對未來的主人翁網開一面。中央政法委在微博公眾號貼文，批評李嘉誠縱容犯罪，不是為香港著想，而是看著香港滑向深淵。<br />\n<br />\n文章反問李嘉誠等「囤地圈錢」的地產商，會否對市民及香港的未來網開一面。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠透過發言人發表聲明回應說，日前的言論被曲解，十分遺憾，並指多年已習慣了那些莫須有的指責，永遠會虛心接受批評，但最重要的是「寬容不等於縱容，不等於無視法律程序」，重申對任何暴力，包括語言暴力，對任何衝擊法治的行為都不能接受。他又希望，各方能尋求空間，而非挑動矛盾，讓香港局勢降溫，社會才可展開對話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480384-20190913.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480384-20190913.htm&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=a050761e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480384-20190913.htm&h=ac9aaa58\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480384-20190913.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b25dbaf01ad33cf5ce9123539355a6cdab9cf923","tid":1565654,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:41:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=11cb80bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"colo